dc_title_s: Chart of the world showing distances saved by the interoceanic canal of Nicaragua and Costa Rica
dc_description_s: Includes "Table showing distances in miles between commercial ports of the world and distances saved by the Nicaragua Canal." 1 map: col.; 54 x 85 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
